==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{countable}} A type of [[headgear]] for [[shield]]ing the eyes from [[glaring]] [[light]], usually consisting of a [[visor]] and a [[headband]], more popular among [[indoor]] workers in the late-nineteenth and early-twentieth centuries than today.
# {{context|not countable}} A [[cosmetic]] product which may be applied to the upper [[eyelid]] and to the area near the [[eye]] to change [[skin]] [[coloration]].

